  "detailed_description": "Put a quarter in the slot and start this arcade up.<br>POGOMAN is a fast paced physics platformer where you use a pogostick to go through weird, hard and precision based levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TIME YOUR JUMPS PERFECTLY</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/6f3907dbb6190bc12906a17b74319ce8.poster.avif?t=1731144922\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/6f3907dbb6190bc12906a17b74319ce8.webm?t=1731144922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/6f3907dbb6190bc12906a17b74319ce8.mp4?t=1731144922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DONT HIT YOUR HEAD (otherwise you explode)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/70785986b030ecb6fa629cf0a9a4e04a.poster.avif?t=1731144922\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/70785986b030ecb6fa629cf0a9a4e04a.webm?t=1731144922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/70785986b030ecb6fa629cf0a9a4e04a.mp4?t=1731144922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLOCK NEW SKILLS</h2>dash, grappling hook, and a pogo gun are all on the table<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/18bdce2688dcb6e7fa224d9e6c6090fd.poster.avif?t=1731144922\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/18bdce2688dcb6e7fa224d9e6c6090fd.webm?t=1731144922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/18bdce2688dcb6e7fa224d9e6c6090fd.mp4?t=1731144922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT GIANT WORMS</h2>Dont ask. The game doesnt have a specific theme or story, I just added what sounded fun.<br>And currently there are only 3 worm levels, but im planning on adding more in the future.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AVOID MISSILES AND MINES... AND METEORS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/d694bce1ab72a035dd18ac9b1eeee558.poster.avif?t=1731144922\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/d694bce1ab72a035dd18ac9b1eeee558.webm?t=1731144922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/d694bce1ab72a035dd18ac9b1eeee558.mp4?t=1731144922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/ffdc2c65d6d6ffa4f986ee28f540e0c3.poster.avif?t=1731144922\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/ffdc2c65d6d6ffa4f986ee28f540e0c3.webm?t=1731144922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/ffdc2c65d6d6ffa4f986ee28f540e0c3.mp4?t=1731144922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>80 LEVELS ON 7 DIFFERENT BIOMES<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190590/extras/af86e5f7e419b42e5163c5c7e5c95c9b.avif?t=1731144922\" width=768 height=432 /></span>",
